<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="whom-pron">whom <strong><em>pron</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /huːm/    美 /huːm/  </p>
<p>[who的宾格，尤用于正式讲话或书面语中]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[疑问代词] 谁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Whom did you see?
你见到了谁?</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Of whom are you speaking?
你说的是谁?</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>[连接代词，引导名词性从句] 谁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Whom your daughter went to the park with is unclear.
你女儿跟谁去的公园还不清楚。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What I want to know is whom we will vote our new monitor. 
我想知道的是我们将选谁当新班长。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[关系代词，引导定语从句] 那些人；他 / 她：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She’s the lady whom we met yesterday.
她就是我们昨天遇到的那位女士。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The man with whom I shook hands just now is an artist.
刚才和我握手的那个人是位画家。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She had a daughter, whom she loved very much.
她有个女儿，她非常爱她的女儿。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Many people, some of whom are not overweight, are going on diets.  
许多人在节食，可其中有些人并没有超重。</p><footer>译林① – 3</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Many young people, most of <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ were well-educated, headed for remote regions to chase their dreams.  （2016 江苏改）  </li>
<li>Have you sent thank-you notes to the relatives from <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ you received gifts?  （2012 上海改）  </li>
<li>In our class there are 46 students, <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ whom half wear glasses.  （2012 四川改）  </li>
<li>She brought with her three friends, none of <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ I had ever met before.  （2009 全国改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. whom  2. whom  3. of  4. whom  </p></div>